              data-full="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate.jpg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-summary">
          <h1>Lathe-Machined Bearing Outer Retainer Plate</h1>
          <p class="product-short-desc">
            Precision-machined bearing outer retainer plate designed for secure bearing
            positioning, structural support, and stable industrial assembly performance.
          </p>

          <div class="product-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="quote-btn">Get a Quote</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/61436605126" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-btn">WhatsApp</a>
          </div>

          <div class="product-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Secure Bearing Positioning</h4>
              <p>Designed to help hold and support bearing outer structures with stability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Precision Machining</h4>
              <p>Manufactured with reliable dimensional consistency for industrial integration.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Custom Manufacturing</h4>
              <p>Suitable for OEM projects, technical drawings, and custom assembly requirements.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Description</h2>
        <p>
          The Lathe-Machined Bearing Outer Retainer Plate is developed for industrial
          applications that require stable bearing support, precise outer positioning,
          and dependable structural fixing. It is suitable for automation equipment,
          mechanical assemblies, and precision machinery systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          With controlled machining accuracy and stable batch consistency, this part can
          be integrated into equipment requiring accurate bearing alignment, secure
          retention, and long-term operational reliability.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Precision lathe-machined for accurate dimensional control</li>
          <li>Designed for bearing outer retention and stable support</li>
          <li>Suitable for custom machinery, OEM products, and industrial assemblies</li>
          <li>Consistent machining quality for repeat production and reliable fit</li>
          <li>Supports customization according to drawings and application requirements</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Technical Advantages</h2>
        <div class="advantage-grid">
          <div class="advantage-card blue">
            <h3>Accurate Fit</h3>
            <p>Stable machining precision helps achieve proper bearing positioning and retention.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card yellow">
            <h3>Reliable Support</h3>
            <p>Built to provide secure structural support for rotating or fixed bearing assemblies.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card green">
            <h3>Flexible Customization</h3>
            <p>Available for OEM production, drawing-based development, and industrial batch supply.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

